data.description: Great starter home! This 3BR/1.5BA home situated in Hidden Valley Lake's private, gated community has updated roof,floor,cabinets, AC unit. Ready for your own personal touch! . It has its own year-round swimming lake and public championship 18-hole golf course with brand-new Greenview Restaurant, Lounge, and Golf Shop. The lake includes two beaches and much more amenities. Nearby schools, shopping and so much more! Just fifteen minutes from Clear Lake and thirty minutes from Calistoga and Northern California's Napa Wine Country!
